channel.title: Owner :: SANS Holiday Hack Challenge 2025
channel.description: Objective Difficulty: 1/5 Help Goose James near the park discover the accidentally leaked SAS token in a public JavaScript file and determine what Azure Storage resource it exposes and what permissions it grants. Goose James mission statement CLUCK CLU… I think I might be losing my mind. All the elves are gone and I’m still hearing voices. The Neighborhood HOA uses Azure for their IT infrastructure.
